I'd like to introduce a fantastic Green Shoes app, <a href="http://jrgifford.github.com/factero/">Factero</a>, created by <a href="https://github.com/jrgifford">James</a>.<p /><em><strong>How do I install on Windows?</strong></em><p />Open your console window and do the following steps:<p />- gem install facter<br />- gem install clipboard<br />- gem install ffi&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; #x86-mingw32<br />- gem install green_shoes<p />- git clone git://github.com/jrgifford/factero.git<br />- cd factero<br />- gshoes main.rb<p />That's all. Let's have fun with Shoes! :-D</p>
<p>ashbb</p>]]></content:encoded>
